Li2 TiuN2-lo2 e5 hui3-mia5 kio3-choe3 Chhun-seng, si7 Ban5 e5 Lou7-kang lang5. I e5 lau7-pe7 u7 si3 e5 kiaN2; i si7 soah-be2 e5. Soe3-han3 e5 si5 chiu7 put-chi2 leng5-khiau2, koh u7 toa7 chi3-khi3, chin khin5 chiu7-kun7 sian-siN bian2-bak8; sou2-i2 u7 the2-tek Tiong-goa7 e5 hak8-bun7, kap thong hiau2 kou2-kim e5 su7-li2. TiuN2-lo2 ti7 siau3-lian5 e5 si5 chiu7 sin3-giong2 Ki-tok-kau3; jin5-keh chin koan5, choe7-choe7 lang5 chun-keng3 i. Ti7 Tong5-ti7 7 ni5 lai5 Tai5-oan5 keng-eng5 te5-siong. Tng-si5 tu2-a2 Tai5-oan5 kap goa7-kok bou7-ek8 choe3 seng7; TiuN2-lo2 m7-na7 lo5-lek8 ti7 siong-kai3, koh siong5-siong5 tu3-su kia3-khi3 Siong7-hai2 e5 po3-koan2, thong-lun7 Chheng-tiau5 te3-cheng3 e5 sit-chhek. Koh chit8-bin7, tui3 i e5 sin3-tek siN-chhut khian5-seng5 e5 sim, long2 bo5 kian3-siau3 i si7 choe3 tong-tai7 it-poaN bin5-chiong3 sou2 kheng-si7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, hoan2-tng2 ho2-taN2 chin7-lat8 soan-thoan5 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 chin-to7. Ia7 kap tng-si5 e5 koaN-hu2 tau3 kou2-bu2 sia7-hoe7 e5 kong-ek su7-giap8, i2-kip8 hong-siok8 e5 kai2-liong5, teng2-teng2.
Ti7 Pak-pou7 chhou-tai7 e5 kau3-hoe7, TiuN2-lo2 si7 chin jiat8-sim e5 chit8-e5.Tui3 Tai5-oan5 jip8 Jit8-pun2 e5 pan2-tou5 liau2-au7, Li2 TiuN2-lo2 tui3 sia7-hoe7 e5 kong3-hian3, sit8-chai7 lan5-tit eng7 pit chit8-hang7 chit8-hang7 lai5 pai5-liat8 kau3 chheng-chho2, chhin tam-tng Tai5-oan5 su2-liau7 phian-chhoan3 pheng5-gi7-oan5 e5 chit lai5 pang-chan7 cheng3-hu2, koh koan-khoan2 lai5 heng-khi2 kau3-iok8, kap choe7-choe7 hang7 e5 chu5-sian7 su7-giap8. Kai Bok8-su teh thoan5-kau3 e5 si5 Li2 TiuN2-lo2 ia7 chin-chiaN3 chin7-lat8 lai5 ui7-tioh8 kau3-hoe7 tioh8-boa5. Au7-lai5 u7 siu7-keng2 choe3 Toa7-tiu7-tiaN5 kau3-hoe7 e5 tiuN2-lo2; mui2 le2-pai3 kau3 pai3-tng5 siu2 an-hioh, jiat8-sim kan-cheng3 to7-li2, gau5 hian2-chhut ho2 bou5-iuN7 lai5 in2-chhoa7 hoe7-iu2, kap chit8-ke e5 hou7-poe3. Koh hian3 gun5 choe7-choe7 lai5 choe3 kian3-tiok pai3-tng5, oh8-tng5 teng2-teng2, kau3-hoe7 su7-giap8 e5 lou7-eng7. Lun7 TiuN2-lo2 e5 kia3-hu3, m7-si7 kan-ta lan2 Pak-pou7 Kau3-hoe7-lai7 chit hong-bin7 na7-tiaN7, chiu7 Loe7-te7-lang5 e5 Kau3-hoe7 kap E7-mng5 e5 Kau3-hoe7 ia7 u7 siu7-tioh8 i chin toa7 e5 pang-chan7.
Li2 TiuN2-lo2 ti7 9 geh8 7 jit8 siu7-chiong hiong2-siu7 88 he3 e5 ko-leng5. I u7 saN e5 kiaN2, chap8-saN e5 sun, koh kau2 e5 cheng-sun. An2-ni thang kong2 i siu7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 chiok-hok sit8-chai7 chin toa7.
